# Weights and models - ignored by extension (small bundled model weights are
# re-included individually below).
*.safetensors
*.gguf
*.bin
*.pt
*.pth
# Bundled model weights (small). Larger nets -- basicvsrpp, the realesrgan RRDBNet x4
# (x4plus/esrnet/bsrgan/bsrnet), fbcnn, nafnet -- are downloaded + converted per each
# weights/README.md, NOT committed (GitHub space). stdf's two 1.4MB files are force-added.
!LTX_2_MLX/videotoolbox/fastdvdnet/weights/*.safetensors
!LTX_2_MLX/videotoolbox/realbasicvsr/weights/*.safetensors
!LTX_2_MLX/videotoolbox/realesrgan/weights/realesr_general_x4v3.safetensors
!LTX_2_MLX/videotoolbox/realesrgan/weights/realesr_general_wdn_x4v3.safetensors
*.ckpt

